         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Hillston ¶ NSW. ¶  ¶ 24 July 1883 ¶ Baron ¶  ¶ Please allow me thank you very sincerely for the — to me very valuable present you were pleased to send me. ¶ Probably B83.03.04.Although reviewed in the...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">83.07.24</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Andrew<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Grant</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M1, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS found with a specimen of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Zygophyllum apiculatum</seg>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(MEL 564666).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>MS annotation by M: 'Answ 29/7/83'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>Hillston<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>NSW.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>24 July 1883</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Please allow me thank you very sincerely for the — to me very valuable present you were pleased to send me.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Probably B83.03.04.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Although reviewed in the metropolitan NSW press, no review has been found in any newspaper published in the Riverina or other country NSW area.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I value it very highly; Firstly as coming from you; secondly as bearing your holograph which will some day be highly prized by the great &amp; good; lastly &amp; most of all for being in the most valued parts the product of your great, fertile and Phylanthropic Brain.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I will try and notice it shortly in one of the local papers</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>A settler brought me the enclosed with a request that I should ask you whether it is poisonous. I think I have seen sheep eat it.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Baron</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your much obliged Servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>A. N. Grant</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Baron Von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
